Insult Trivia

Mod 1 Flatiron project. Brittan Fairchild and Ellyn Anderson

Welcome to the Insult Trivia! Weâ€™re glad to see brave souls eager to learn.
Upon entering the game, you must type your name and it will be saved to our database.
Press play and get going. There are many categories of questions (generated randomly each time), and a multiple choice layout. Press 1, 2, 3 or 4 to choose. Only one answer is correct, of course, and Insult Trivia is eager to tell you when you are wrong.
Upon completion of the game, you receive:
	-Score for current game
	-Your aggregated score for all games
	-Top players and scores of all time